item.description: I am a computer science engineer specializing in predictive analytics applications. Presently working in fire and life safety research to design and implement data science solutions, analytical processes and encourage data driven decisions within the organization. Previously trained in business intelligence and data warehousing tools where I built data processing pipelines and KPI dashboards for big data and business teams in IT organizations. Interests: Deep Learning, Natural Language Processing, Distributed Frameworks
